OL,3,CAttorney general blames collapse of
OL,4,CChina spy trial on outdated laws
OL,6,FAttorney General Lord Richard Hermer
OL,7,Fhas told a committee of MPs he blamed
OL,8,Fan "out of date" and "not fit for
OL,9,Fpurpose" law for the collapse of the
OL,10,Ftrial of two men accused of spying for
OL,11,FChina.
OL,13,FSpeaking to the National Security
OL,14,FStrategy Committee on Wednesday, Lord
OL,15,FHermer said he believed prosecutors
OL,16,Fhad worked in "good faith" to secure
OL,17,Fconvictions against Christopher Cash
OL,18,Fand Christopher Berry, but the
OL,19,FOfficial Secrets Act 1911 posed a
OL,20,F"very significant problem".
