OL,6,FChristopher Cash, a former
OL,7,Fparliamentary researcher, and
OL,8,FChristopher Berry, a teacher were
OL,9,Fcharged under the Official Secrets Act
OL,10,F1911 in April 2024, as was the law at
OL,11,Fthe time the offences took place.
OL,13,FBoth men denied any wrongdoing.
OL,15,FThe government's top law officer said
OL,16,Fhe had "no doubt" the case would have
OL,17,Fgone to trial if legislation had been
OL,18,Fupdated during the period of alleged
OL,19,Foffending between 2021 and 2023.
