OL,6,FHe said: "Standing back in this case,
OL,7,Fwhere's the problem? What is it ?
OL,8,FBecause I think we should all be
OL,9,Fconcerned to try and identify what
OL,10,Flessons can be learnt.
OL,12,F"I'm clear in my mind that certainly
OL,13,Fone very significant problem here was
OL,14,Fthe Act. The Act wasn't fit for
OL,15,Fpurpose, it was out of date."
