OL,6,FLord Hermer said the National Security
OL,7,FAct 2023 had addressed problems with
OL,8,Fthe Official Secrets Act by replacing
OL,9,Fthe term "enemy" with a requirement
OL,10,Ffor prosecutors to prove that
OL,11,F"information was being passed to a
OL,12,Fforeign power".
OL,14,FHe told the committee on Wednesday:
OL,15,F"Speaking frankly, I don't understand
OL,16,Fwhy it took Parliament so long to pass
OL,17,Fthat.
