OL,6,FAttention was focused on the
OL,7,Fstatements of Deputy National Security
OL,8,FAdviser Matt Collins, with prosecutors
OL,9,Fsaying his refusal to describe Beijing
OL,10,Fas a "threat" to national security
OL,11,Fmeant the case could not continue.
OL,13,FOn Monday, the senior official said he
OL,14,Fhad provided evidence of a "range of
OL,15,Fthreats" posed by China but had not
OL,16,Fdescribed the country as a "generic"
OL,17,Fthreat because that was not the
OL,18,Fposition of the then-Tory government.
