OL,6,FUnder the old Official Secrets Act,
OL,7,Fthe CPS felt such a description would
OL,8,Fhave been required to successfully
OL,9,Fprosecute following an earlier legal
OL,10,Fruling which set such a precedent.
OL,12,FSpeaking on Wednesday, Lord Hermer
OL,13,Fconcurred that Conservative leader
OL,14,FKemi Badenoch's assertion, when she
OL,15,Fwas business secretary, that Beijing
OL,16,Fshould not be described as a "foe"
OL,17,Fwould have undermined the
OL,18,Fprosecution's case at trial.
