OL,6,FThe government have instead sought to
OL,7,Fblame the Conservatives who were in
OL,8,Foffice at the time of the alleged
OL,9,Foffences, and who they say failed to
OL,10,Fupdate the law sufficiently during
OL,11,Ftheir time in power.
OL,13,FOn Tuesday, a letter was published
OL,14,Ffrom Lord Carlile KC, a former
OL,15,Fcriminal barrister and independent
OL,16,Freviewer of terrorism legislation, in
OL,17,Fwhuch he claimed the DPP had made "an
OL,18,Fincorrect decision" in concluding
OL,19,Fthere was insufficient evidence to
OL,20,Fprosecute the case.
